00:17:29.437 --> 00:17:30.638 position:5% line:89% align:start
Well, even if no one's here,

00:17:30.738 --> 00:17:33.809 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'd still like to leave some
money for them.

00:17:37.181 --> 00:17:38.282 position:5% line:89% align:start
Um...

00:17:38.381 --> 00:17:40.152 position:5% line:83% align:start
Would you mind paying
for me, Tomoya?

00:17:40.252 --> 00:17:42.255 position:5% line:83% align:start
What's wrong?
You don't have any cash?

00:17:42.354 --> 00:17:43.555 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Nagisa] I do...

00:17:43.655 --> 00:17:46.327 position:5% line:83% align:start
but I'd like you to pay
if that's all right.

00:17:46.426 --> 00:17:48.195 position:5% line:89% align:start
Um, do you mind?

00:17:48.295 --> 00:17:50.232 position:5% line:83% align:start
Nope, don't mind at all.
How much?

00:17:50.332 --> 00:17:52.201 position:5% line:89% align:start
It's 120 yen.

00:17:52.301 --> 00:17:53.236 position:5% line:89% align:start
Here!

00:17:53.336 --> 00:17:55.905 position:5% line:89% align:start
Perfect, thank you very much.

00:17:56.006 --> 00:17:58.675 position:5% line:83% align:start
Oh, how nice of you
to treat me, Tomoya!

00:17:58.775 --> 00:18:01.347 position:5% line:83% align:start
What are you talking about?
You MADE me pay.

00:18:01.446 --> 00:18:04.884 position:5% line:77% align:start
[Nagisa]
But it's okay, because I know
you won't be upset about it.

00:18:04.984 --> 00:18:06.286 position:5% line:89% align:start
And why's that?

00:18:06.385 --> 00:18:08.256 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Nagisa] Well...

00:18:08.356 --> 00:18:10.124 position:5% line:89% align:start
Because it's for me, right?

00:18:10.224 --> 00:18:12.227 position:5% line:89% align:start
Huh? Hold on a second.

00:18:12.327 --> 00:18:13.362 position:5% line:89% align:start
You mind repeating that for me?

00:18:13.461 --> 00:18:15.797 position:5% line:83% align:start
I can, but I really
don't want to.

00:18:15.899 --> 00:18:18.568 position:5% line:83% align:start
No, I really didn't
understand you.

00:18:18.668 --> 00:18:20.604 position:5% line:89% align:start
Oh, I see. Well, in that case,

00:18:20.704 --> 00:18:23.241 position:5% line:83% align:start
I guess I have no choice
but to say it again.

00:18:23.341 --> 00:18:25.644 position:5% line:89% align:start
(deep breath)

00:18:25.744 --> 00:18:27.513 position:5% line:89% align:start
Listen closely this time.

00:18:27.613 --> 00:18:28.781 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Tomoya] Okay.

00:18:28.882 --> 00:18:30.284 position:5% line:83% align:start
What I said was,
I know you won't be upset

00:18:30.385 --> 00:18:34.088 position:5% line:83% align:start
because you're buying
the bread for me!

00:18:34.189 --> 00:18:37.459 position:5% line:83% align:start
I said it pretty loud.
You heard me that time, right?

00:18:37.559 --> 00:18:39.095 position:5% line:89% align:start
Uh, yeah, I heard you.

00:18:39.195 --> 00:18:43.634 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Nagisa] Good, I was afraid
I'd have to say it louder.

00:18:44.269 --> 00:18:45.536 position:5% line:89% align:start
So is it good?

00:18:45.637 --> 00:18:48.241 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm so nervous right now,
I can't eveb taste it.

00:18:48.341 --> 00:18:50.210 position:5% line:83% align:start
What's there to be
nervous about?

00:18:50.311 --> 00:18:52.179 position:5% line:89% align:start
Oh, I forgot to say my line!

00:18:52.279 --> 00:18:57.386 position:5% line:77% align:start
Let's see... Since you bought it
for me, it's, uh, even more
delicious than usual.

00:18:57.485 --> 00:18:59.355 position:5% line:89% align:start
Well, I'm glad to hear it.

00:18:59.455 --> 00:19:01.892 position:5% line:83% align:start
You're supposed to ask
for a bite, Tomoya.

00:19:01.992 --> 00:19:04.162 position:5% line:83% align:start
It doesn't really work when
you tell me what I want.

00:19:04.262 --> 00:19:06.965 position:5% line:83% align:start
Okay, then I'll try to make
it like a question.

00:19:07.066 --> 00:19:09.402 position:5% line:83% align:start
Tomoya, would you like
to have a bite?

00:19:09.501 --> 00:19:10.837 position:5% line:89% align:start
Not really.

00:19:10.937 --> 00:19:13.506 position:5% line:83% align:start
You're really making this
tough on me.

00:19:13.606 --> 00:19:16.077 position:5% line:83% align:start
So I supposed to say,  yes ?
I get it.

00:19:16.178 --> 00:19:17.312 position:5% line:89% align:start
Would you like to have a bite?

00:19:17.412 --> 00:19:19.982 position:5% line:89% align:start
Yeah, I REALLY wanna bite!

00:19:20.083 --> 00:19:21.117 position:5% line:89% align:start
Really? For real?!

00:19:21.217 --> 00:19:23.921 position:5% line:83% align:start
Sorry, but you can't have any!
[TOMOYA] (d'oh!)

00:19:24.021 --> 00:19:27.125 position:5% line:83% align:start
Oh, are you okay, Tomoya?!
What's wrong?

00:19:27.225 --> 00:19:28.493 position:5% line:89% align:start
Why can't I have any?

00:19:28.593 --> 00:19:31.430 position:5% line:83% align:start
Because... because I don't
have enough to share.

00:19:31.530 --> 00:19:32.698 position:5% line:89% align:start
Fine, then just forget about it.

00:19:32.798 --> 00:19:34.234 position:5% line:89% align:start
That won't do at all!

00:19:34.334 --> 00:19:36.270 position:5% line:83% align:start
We'll just have to come up with
a way for you to enjoy it

00:19:36.371 --> 00:19:37.638 position:5% line:89% align:start
without eating it.

00:19:37.739 --> 00:19:39.108 position:5% line:89% align:start
Well, whatever makes you happy.

00:19:39.208 --> 00:19:42.379 position:5% line:83% align:start
Okay, then try turning
your head toward me.

00:19:42.479 --> 00:19:43.813 position:5% line:89% align:start
You mean, like this?

00:19:43.913 --> 00:19:45.749 position:5% line:89% align:start
Perfect!

00:19:46.350 --> 00:19:47.251 position:5% line:89% align:start
(ahh...)

00:19:47.351 --> 00:19:50.856 position:5% line:89% align:start
(breaths out softly)

00:19:52.859 --> 00:19:56.296 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Nagisa] Um, how was that?

00:19:56.397 --> 00:20:00.268 position:5% line:83% align:start
You were supposed to get a nice
whiff of my cinnamon roll.

00:20:01.437 --> 00:20:04.540 position:5% line:83% align:start
Tomoya, don't just stare!
Say somthing!

00:20:04.640 --> 00:20:07.512 position:5% line:83% align:start
If you keep looking at me
like that, I'm gonna cry.

00:20:07.611 --> 00:20:09.981 position:5% line:83% align:start
Hey, Mei, I see you!
[Nagisa] (startled)

00:20:10.615 --> 00:20:11.849 position:5% line:89% align:start
(giggles)

00:20:11.950 --> 00:20:14.387 position:5% line:83% align:start
You can't trick me.
I knew this was your idea!

00:20:14.487 --> 00:20:16.623 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Mei] You figured it out, huh?

00:20:16.723 --> 00:20:20.895 position:5% line:77% align:start
Of course I did!
No matter how you look at it,
it was way too forced.

00:20:20.995 --> 00:20:24.566 position:5% line:83% align:start
Operation Date is complete!
Mei, signing off!

00:20:24.666 --> 00:20:26.002 position:5% line:89% align:start
(giggles)

00:20:26.102 --> 00:20:29.273 position:5% line:83% align:start
Come back here, you brat!
[Nagisa] Okazaki!

00:20:29.373 --> 00:20:30.974 position:5% line:89% align:start
That little punk!

00:20:31.076 --> 00:20:34.045 position:5% line:83% align:start
I don't get it. Was Mei
blackmailing you or something?

00:20:34.146 --> 00:20:35.181 position:5% line:89% align:start
Is that it?

00:20:35.281 --> 00:20:39.686 position:5% line:83% align:start
Oh, no, it's nothing like that.
I just...

00:20:39.786 --> 00:20:41.522 position:5% line:89% align:start
Did she say something to you?

00:20:41.621 --> 00:20:42.890 position:5% line:89% align:start
She said...

00:20:42.990 --> 00:20:44.993 position:5% line:83% align:start
you were selfconscious about
being a delinquent,

00:20:45.094 --> 00:20:47.297 position:5% line:83% align:start
so you don't want to force
yourself on me.

00:20:47.397 --> 00:20:52.069 position:5% line:77% align:start
And since I'm older than you
are, I should be taking the
initiative in our relationship.

00:20:52.169 --> 00:20:54.272 position:5% line:83% align:start
Yeah, I figured it was
something like that.

00:20:54.372 --> 00:20:59.112 position:5% line:77% align:start
[Nagisa] I was trying to follow
the plan that Mei wrote, but I
kept messing it up.

00:20:59.212 --> 00:21:03.251 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry, this was
really dumb of me.

00:21:03.750 --> 00:21:06.087 position:5% line:89% align:start
Yeah, I agree.

00:21:06.188 --> 00:21:10.393 position:5% line:83% align:start
After all that, I wouldn't blame
you if you hated me. (huh)

00:21:10.494 --> 00:21:13.297 position:5% line:83% align:start
I wouldn't hate you for all
the bad dates in the world.

00:21:13.397 --> 00:21:18.103 position:5% line:77% align:start
Besides, even if her methods
were off, I think Mei was
right in a way.

00:21:18.203 --> 00:21:21.174 position:5% line:83% align:start
You know, the day's not over
just yet. You have a sec?

00:21:21.274 --> 00:21:24.645 position:5% line:83% align:start
Um, well, I guess I might a
little more time before dinner.

00:21:24.745 --> 00:21:28.917 position:5% line:77% align:start
In that case, why don't you
and I take a little walk
to work up our appetite.

00:21:29.718 --> 00:21:31.320 position:5% line:89% align:start
Where do you want to go?

00:21:31.421 --> 00:21:34.592 position:5% line:89% align:start
A-anywhere's okay with me.

00:21:34.691 --> 00:21:38.029 position:5% line:89% align:start
I mean, as long as I'm with you.

00:21:39.865 --> 00:21:41.535 position:5% line:89% align:start
Glad to hear it.

00:21:41.635 --> 00:21:43.336 position:5% line:89% align:start
Then, uh...

00:21:46.374 --> 00:21:48.977 position:5% line:89% align:start
let's stay together forever.

00:23:42.326 --> 00:23:44.861 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Tomoya] <i>It's been a month</i>
 <i>since I started dating Tomoyo.</i>

00:23:44.961 --> 00:23:46.765 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>It wasn't really planned</i>
 <i>or anything.</i>

00:23:46.864 --> 00:23:48.267 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>It just sort of happened.</i>

00:23:48.367 --> 00:23:50.969 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>When I first met her,</i>
 <i>I was always cutting class.</i>

00:23:51.070 --> 00:23:52.972 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>Even when I did come to school,</i>
 <i>I was late.</i>

00:23:53.073 --> 00:23:55.443 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>But somehow, after getting to</i>
 <i>know her better,</i>

00:23:55.543 --> 00:23:58.046 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>not only did I start coming</i>
 <i>to school on time,</i>

00:23:58.146 --> 00:23:59.649 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>I started falling in love</i>
 <i>with her as well.</i>

00:23:59.749 --> 00:24:03.920 position:5% line:83% align:start
Tomoya, you'll stay with me
from now on too, won't you?

00:24:04.020 --> 00:24:05.724 position:5% line:89% align:start
Yeah, of course.

00:24:05.824 --> 00:24:07.826 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Guy] You realize the
situation, don't you?

00:24:07.925 --> 00:24:10.996 position:5% line:83% align:start
You understand what kind
of person she is.

